songs.title: Thought Bubbles (Reprise)
songs.lyrics:
[JOSH, spoken]
17, 18, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 24

[ANNA]
Thought bubbles in your mind!

[JOSH, spoken]
Ok, uh... 21, 22, 23...

[ANNA]
Poppin' those bubbles from time to time

[JOSH, spoken]
Dammit! Okay... 1, 2, 3, 4, 5...

[ANNA]
You don't have to be alone with your thoughts

(spoken)
Call me
